      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">235.070-3</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p>When the contractor is to be indemnified in accordance with 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="i1380230" href="235.070-1.dita#DFARS_235.070-1">235.070-1</xref>
            , use either—</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a)  The clause at 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="i1383375" href="252.235-7000.dita#DFARS_252.235-7000">252.235-7000</xref>
            , Indemnification Under 10 U.S.C. 2354—Fixed Price; or</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b)  The clause at 
               <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly" base="i1383384" href="252.235-7001.dita#DFARS_252.235-7001">252.235-7001</xref>
            , Indemnification Under 10 U.S.C. 2354—Cost-Reimbursement, as appropriate.</p>
